Class AbstractUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glyptodon.guacamole.net.auth.AbstractUser

    public abstract class AbstractUser
extends Object
implements User
    Basic implementation of a Guacamole user which uses the username to determine equality. Username comparison is case-sensitive.
